'''Germany''' has a comparably wide spread [[veganism|vegan]] culture. Especially in cities like [[Berlin]] and [[Hamburg]] there are lots of options for vegans. Other places in Germany has quite some options, too. [[Dortmund]] was for example the location for "Europe's biggest" vegan supermarket at one point in history.


