The '''United States''' is a land of extremes. You can find gigantic unhealthy portions of dead animals in most restaurants but it's probably also the country with the best options for [[veganism|vegans]]. [[New York City|New York]] and [[San Francisco]] are home to some of the best vegan restaurants in the world. And you can find [[veganaise]] and tons of [[vegan meat substitutes]] in fairly average supermarkets.


