==Vegan restaurants==
There are at least two vegan fast food places.

* [http://www.vleischerei.de/ Vleischerei] is one such vegan fast food place. It smells authentically of deep fried unhealthy food but the food is excellent (and less unhealthy than almost any other place that smells like this). (Closed on Mondays.)


